Managing and disabling cookies
Any cookie that is not Strictly Necessary is not active by default and does not send information to the resource it is called from. Accepting all cookies, makes all cookies active. You can modify your cookie preferences for the website at any time by clicking on the ‘Cookie Settings’ button below.
Cookie Settings
Your Rights and Personal Data
As a Mentor Books Ltd customer, website user or business contact, you may request a copy of your Personal Data held by us. You also have the right to correct any inaccuracies in your Personal Data,
object to certain uses of your Personal Data and to request deletion of your Personal Data. Where Mentor Books Ltd is relying on your consent to process your Personal Data, you have the right to
withdraw your consent by writing to the address specified below. Any of these rights can be exercised by writing to us at the address and/or email address specified below.
You also have the right to make a complaint about the processing of your Personal Data by Mentor Books Ltd with the Data Protection Commission at
info@dataprotection.ie
or by writing to:
Data Protection Commissioner, 21 Fitzwilliam Square South, Dublin 2.
Contact us:
If you have any queries in relation to our processing of your Personal Data or in relation to this Privacy Policy please contact us by email at
admin@mentorbooks.ie
or write to us at:
MentorBooks Ltd, 43 Furze Road, Sandyford Industrial Estate, Dublin 18
